Al Shami is a new voice of the Arab world, born in Syria and raised through challenges that shaped his art and his vision. His journey reflects resilience, ambition, and creativity, and his music continues to inspire, unite, and push Arab sound into the future.

To create my videos, I spend a lot of time building maps, creating a plot, arranging cameras in an in-game editor, recording, editing and previews for videos.
